{{Vgname|水滸傳·天命之誓|ja=水滸伝・天命の誓い|en=Bandit Kings of Ancient China|diff=yes}}是[[光榮株式會社|光榮株式會社]]於1989年推出的[[回合制策略遊戲|回合制策略遊戲]]<ref>{{cite web|first=Andrew |last=Vestal |title=The History of Console RPGs |publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |date=1998-11-02 |url=http://uk.gamespot.com/features/vgs/universal/rpg_hs/nes8.html |accessdate=2011-01-06 |ref=gspot_consolehist |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110711072705/http://uk.gamespot.com/features/vgs/universal/rpg_hs/nes8.html |archivedate=2011-07-11 }}</ref>，參照中國文學名著《[[水滸傳|水滸傳]]》為基礎來設計遊戲內容，並加入了若干的新元素。遊戲後來大量移植或復刻到各種平台上<ref>{{Cite book |title=''Bandit Kings of Ancient China'' for PC |publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |accessdate=2009-02-02 |url=http://www.gamespot.com/pc/strategy/banditkingsofancientchina/index.html |archive-date=2009-08-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090830194401/http://www.gamespot.com/pc/strategy/banditkingsofancientchina/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite book |title=''Bandit Kings of Ancient China'' for AMI |publisher=GameSpot |accessdate=2009-02-02 |url=http://www.gamespot.com/amiga/strategy/banditkingsofancientchina/index.html}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|title=Bandit Kings of Ancient China for NES |publisher=GameSpot |accessdate=2009-02-02 |url=http://www.gamespot.com/nes/strategy/banditkingsofancientchina/index.html |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090304161342/http://www.gamespot.com/nes/strategy/banditkingsofancientchina/index.html |archivedate=2009-03-04|deadurl=no }}</ref>，而圖像及[[音效|音效]]亦得到大幅的改善<ref>{{cite news |title=光榮水滸傳天命之誓 - FC版與PS重製版比較圖 |url=http://home.gamer.com.tw/creationDetail.php?sn=339692 |language=zh |author=又回歸人間的老骨灰 |publisher=巴哈姆特電玩資訊站 |date=2009-10-25 |accessdate=2015-08-13 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304054049/http://home.gamer.com.tw/creationDetail.php?sn=339692 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 遊戲方式 ==
遊戲採用回合制，以1127年[[靖康之變|金兵入侵大宋]]之前得到聖旨打敗奸臣[[高俅|高俅]]為目標<ref>{{Cite book |last=Baker |first=Christopher |title=allgame ((( Bandit Kings of Ancient China > Overview ))) |publisher=[[Allgame|Allgame]] |accessdate=2009-02-02 |url=http://www.allgame.com/cg/agg.dll?p=agg&sql=1:14476}}</ref>。玩家需要不斷與接鄰的官兵及群豪戰鬥以擴充自己的版圖，涉及徵兵、練兵、打獵、耕種、買賣米糧獸皮、打造兵器、任命太守等細節，亦需要應付隨機發生於各屬地的天災人禍。

== 反響 ==
多個媒體普遍對遊戲有正面的評價，《[[任天堂力量|任天堂力量]]》（{{lang|en|Nintendo Power}}）雖然對回合的步調有所保留，但是仍然認為玩家會喜歡它的深度、參與度和對細節的注重程度<ref>{{cite journal|title=Now playing: Bandit Kings of Ancient China|work=[[Nintendo_Power|Nintendo Power]]|volume=22|pages=74–75|date=March 1991}}</ref>。《Compute!》雜誌則認為它是當時眾多回合制策略遊戲中，最完整和最有趣的一個遊戲<ref>{{cite journal|last=Du Gaue |first=Robert |url=http://www.atarimagazines.com/compute/issue128/94_Bandit_Kings_of_Anci.php |title=Bandit Kings of Ancient China |work={{tsl|en|Compute!|}} |issue=128 |page=94 |date=April 1991 |accessdate=2009-02-03 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090201020804/http://www.atarimagazines.com/compute/issue128/94_Bandit_Kings_of_Anci.php |archivedate=2009-02-01|deadurl=no }}</ref>，在1991年電腦推薦大獎（{{lang|en|Compute Choice Awards}}）亦榜上有名<ref>{{cite journal|url=http://www.atarimagazines.com/compute/issue125/12_The_1991_Compute_Cho.php|title=The 1991 Compute Choice Awards|work={{tsl|en|Compute!|}}|issue=125|page=12|date=January 1991|accessdate=2009-09-11|journal=|archive-date=2011-05-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110524190607/http://www.atarimagazines.com/compute/issue125/12_The_1991_Compute_Cho.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[電腦遊戲世界|電腦遊戲世界]]》於1996年將遊戲內的高俅評為「最令人印象深刻的壞蛋」的第十二位<ref>{{cite news|title=The 15 most memorable game villains|work=[[Computer_Gaming_World|Computer Gaming World]]|url=http://www.cgwmuseum.org/galleries/issues/cgw_148.pdf|publisher=Golden Empire Publications Inc|date=November 1996|accessdate=18 November 2013|page=121|archive-date=2013-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130511185822/http://www.cgwmuseum.org/galleries/issues/cgw_148.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

